      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CLARICE (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in 10 starts, including four wins and six placings. Hit the frame latest (30.28) when second at this track in a Grade 5. With a clean break looks hard to beat. RAMIREZ MONELLI (1) collided in the run last time but kept coming to hit the frame in a Novice race at this track (30.39). Harder here but expected to measure up. JUST A SAPPHIRE (7) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten half a length, (29.95) at this track. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Overdue and expected to feature again. GRAVITY MONELLI (4) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.",
